# Todo Python Service

This is the Todo microservice in Python with Flask.

## Docker Commands to Run the Container

1. Build the image:
   docker build -t todo-service .

2. Run the container:
   docker run -p 3000:3000 todo-service

3. Check running containers:
   docker ps

4. Check all containers:
   docker ps -a

5. See logs:
   docker logs <CONTAINER ID>

6. Stop a container:
   docker stop <CONTAINER ID>

7. List images:
   docker images